text.title: Cara
text.tspan: Wahhh! I can't do this anymore.
I'm a 3L. I shouldn't be studying.

text.title: Cara
text.tspan: I should be, like, rocking out

text.title: Cara
text.tspan: But I want to do well on this
exam. I really like this professor!

text.title: Cara
text.tspan: Because I'm not. I'm just graduating.

text.title: Cara
text.tspan: Unless I fail. Which I might if I--

text.title: Tort Bunny
text.tspan: Try and give less of a shit.
Cite as: Andrew Fong, Final Stretch, TORT BUNNIES (May 7, 2012), http://tortbunnies.com/157.html.
